node.text: The living legend @MikeHornExplorer tells us about the horrible scenes he has witnessed during his adventures and the importance of the young generations in the race to save our planet ! We must all get together now and start moving, it’s time for action ! Our special thanks to @spgrytz for supporting our vision towards a sustainable environment! #DiscoverEarth

node.text:
Meet Meayunan, a traditional swing game of Tenganan, Bali 😍

Traditions have been handed down from generation to generation in Tenganan Village, including this swing game. This tradition is only played once every year, but it’s not just for entertainment – the swing’s spinning symbolises life’s cycle and the way it continues to swing up and down.

Insider tip: If you’d like to witness Meayunan, visit Tenganan Village during the Usabha Sambah ritual, which is held in the fifth month of the village’s calendar.

📍Tenganan, Bali, Indonesia

🇮🇩 #discoverIndonesia with @juni_newman

node.text:
An ice cave glowing like amber from the golden rays of a setting sun. ✨

“The golden rays of the sunset entered the cave at just the right angle to light up this section of ice, making it look like amber. It was so a bright orange stripe running along the wall of the ice cave. Definitely one of the more unique things I have seen” says @sarah.bethea

We are also obsessed with the sunrays on this cave…and if you’re planning to go to Iceland, make sure to visit the country’s stunning ice caves ❄️

Insider tip: While in Iceland, why not organise a whale watching tour or a trip to the beautiful waterfalls and mysterious lakes of Iceland? 🐋

📍 Iceland

🇮🇸 #discoverIceland with @sarah.bethea

node.text:
Have to love their curiosity and confidence 🐘

Sri Lankan elephants are the largest species of Asian elephants. While they grow up to be quite big, they always remain playful (and incredibly cute!), and just like every other species, they also deserve our care and attention. Since the 19th century, their population have almost fallen 65%, which led them to be protected under the Sri Lankan law.

Who else wishes they could spot an elephant while on holiday to Sri Lanka? 🍃

📍Sri Lanka 

🇱🇰 #discoverSriLanka with @thissrilankangirl

node.text:
Off to an epic adventure with @gossegoss and the most perfect hiking buddy 🍃🐕

“Geiranger is one of Norways most beautiful places… we ended up having Skageflå, which is one of the most popular hikes all to ourselves. Videos and pictures will never do this place justice though, and it is popular for a reason! I just can’t believe how lucky we got”

We couldn’t agree more with Lene – this village is located on one of the world’s most spectacular fjords, with so many beautiful waterfall and cliffside views! Would you visit Geiranger?

📍 Geiranger, Norway

🇳🇴 #discoverNorway with @gossegoss
